{"TopicId":197799,"ForumId":66,"TopicTitle":"KSP Loading...Preview: New Lights!","CreatedByName":"St4rdust","CreatedById":196576,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-29T21:02:36Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"St4rdust","CreatedById":196576,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-29T21:02:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align: justify;\u0022\u003E\nLights, camera, action! Be ready for new Light Parts \u0026amp; Light Changes in 1.11 update!\u003Cbr\u003E\nTo help craft builders add more variety to their craft, we will add some new lights to the game. Now you can add more customization, especially in small crafts.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align: justify;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.reddit.com/r/KerbalSpaceProgram/comments/jkio90/lights_camera_action_be_ready_for_new_light_parts/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EImage HQ\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/monthly_2020_10/ksploading_lights_small.png.93a4762eef481104511bfea74225633b.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsAttachLink ipsAttachLink_image\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg data-fileid=\u0022276\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/monthly_2020_10/ksploading_lights_small.thumb.png.2ff8b1261e4f3f2cace84f9ed7405cc9.png\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022121.42\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 alt=\u0022ksploading_lights_small.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-29T21:05:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOooh love the work lamps, will they function like the deployable science experiments? I thought the stock inventory system needed more stuff.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ElWanderer","CreatedById":114015,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-29T21:09:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis makes me very happy. I guess the work lights will be good for setting up screenshots\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NoMrBond","CreatedById":69263,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-29T21:12:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLight changes?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs KSP\u0027s lighting [system, and associated modules] being updated (now possible because of the new single camera system I\u0027m guessing)?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-10-29T21:31:24Z\u0022 title=\u002210/29/2020 09:31  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 29, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by NoMrBond\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Equestion clarity\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Frank_G","CreatedById":100000,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-29T21:18:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNice touch. This will add a lot of character to upcoming spaceship designs \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VoidCosmos","CreatedById":192336,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-29T21:29:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI smell something to do with mining!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KeaKaka","CreatedById":202882,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-29T21:31:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNice! I was just wondering about lights yesterday, this is a great thing to see in stock!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWill the current lights also get texture switches and colour changes?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GuessingEveryDay","CreatedById":203507,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-29T21:33:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr maybe an overhaul of aviation parts! The wings are pretty old.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*Research hours later*\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWow... They\u0027ve been in the game since 0.15.\u00A0 But I can\u0027t find when they changed the look.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NoMrBond","CreatedById":69263,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-29T21:40:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223874810\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197799\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221604007201\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022203507\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022GuessingEveryDay\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, GuessingEveryDay said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWow... They\u0027ve been in the game since 0.15.\u00A0 But I can\u0027t find when they changed the look.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen Porkjets SPP was integrated into the game in 0.25\u00A0(I think?)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-29T22:09:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRave rocket incoming!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Maxsimal","CreatedById":160254,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-29T22:14:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-gramm=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223874793\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197799\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221604005527\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Superfluous J\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Superfluous J said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022 data-gramm=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOooh love the work lamps, will they function like the deployable science experiments? I thought the stock inventory system needed more stuff.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes they\u0027re deployable like the BG parts.\u00A0 The inventory system released with BG has always been part of the stock game code (in case modders wanted to use it), it was just not turned on in the UI because there weren\u0027t any stock parts that\u0027d go in an inventory before.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-10-29T22:15:36Z\u0022 title=\u002210/29/2020 10:15  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 29, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Maxsimal\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fourfa","CreatedById":151713,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-29T22:47:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo I spy tiny solar panels on the work lights? So they just work anywhere, and don\u2019t have to tie into the science power system?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Justadutchguy","CreatedById":197333,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-29T22:51:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh so nice! Now I can make awesome window ports in my builds!\u003Cimg alt=\u0022cLP59WO.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/cLP59WO.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lewie","CreatedById":203745,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-29T22:51:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMan, this has got to be a record for announcements!\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHype. What else is there to say?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-29T23:00:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes! We needed this \u003Cspan\u003E:D!\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dat Kerbal Dude","CreatedById":206145,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-29T23:01:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFinally, i can make fake M\u00FCn Landing video clips!\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:lol:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/default_laugh.png\u0022 title=\u0022:lol:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Maxsimal","CreatedById":160254,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-29T23:44:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-gramm=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223874851\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197799\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221604011670\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022151713\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022fourfa\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n56 minutes ago, fourfa said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022 data-gramm=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo I spy tiny solar panels on the work lights? So they just work anywhere, and don\u2019t have to tie into the science power system?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s right, you won\u0027t need those parts from BG to use these.\u00A0 \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Raptor9","CreatedById":67915,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-30T00:46:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI foresee Kerbal street racers on the runway using those light strips.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RyanRising","CreatedById":79932,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-30T00:49:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223874810\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197799\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221604007201\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022203507\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022GuessingEveryDay\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, GuessingEveryDay said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr maybe an overhaul of aviation parts! The wings are pretty old.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*Research hours later*\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWow... They\u0027ve been in the game since 0.15.\u00A0 But I can\u0027t find when they changed the look.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223874815\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197799\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221604007603\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002269263\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022NoMrBond\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, NoMrBond said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen Porkjets SPP was integrated into the game in 0.25\u00A0(I think?)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIMO pretty much all of Porkjet\u0027s work stands up really well. There are things that I\u0027d like changed about wings (pwings perhaps), but their look isn\u0027t really one of them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-30T02:38:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223874854\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197799\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221604011904\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022203745\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lewie\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Lewie said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMan, this has got to be a record for announcements!\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHype. What else is there to say?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nActually when Breaking Ground was being teased they did an update almost every single day. But I like this announcement!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Yellowburn10","CreatedById":107558,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-30T03:28:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVery nice touch, it always slightly bothered me that in terms of lighting we really only had a big light, a slightly bigger light, and landing gear light.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"R-T-B","CreatedById":200868,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-30T05:45:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlease tell me you guys are finally switching to deferred rendering with this update...\u00A0 the forward rendering system you are using now for lighting is pretty painful to work with.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Random Annoying Guy","CreatedById":202206,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-30T07:19:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223874836\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197799\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221604009695\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160254\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Maxsimal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 hours ago, Maxsimal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes they\u0027re deployable like the BG parts.\u00A0 The inventory system released with BG has always been part of the stock game code (in case modders wanted to use it), it was just not turned on in the UI because there weren\u0027t any stock parts that\u0027d go in an inventory before.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWAIT WHAT\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-30T07:55:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh wow, this was really unexpected but really cool! I can\u0027t wait to set up a few of these around my Mun base \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223874891\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197799\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221604015096\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160254\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Maxsimal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, Maxsimal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s right, you won\u0027t need those parts from BG to use these.\u00A0 \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat about powering them during the night, when solar power isn\u0027t available? Can we still link them up to a BG \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Radio-isotope Thermo-electric Generator (a.k.a. Mars rover heating device)\u0022\u003ERTG\u003C/abbr\u003E if we want? Do they have some kind of small internal batteries?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-30T09:51:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. Do they turn in pumpkins every Halloween?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022image.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002265.63\u0022 height=\u0022210\u0022 width=\u0022320\u0022 src=\u0022https://media.timeout.com/images/105697639/320/210/image.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\n2. A handheld electrodynamical flashlight for Kerbals.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTgY_7UGPPN6pruqyaylXa\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.55\u0022 height=\u0022183\u0022 width=\u0022275\u0022 src=\u0022https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTgY_7UGPPN6pruqyaylXaCVxKBtGNpfWmFpA\u0026amp;usqp=CAU\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nQuickly press U-U-U-U-U-U-... to get the light.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\n3. Can the lights power the solar arrays to get EC to power the lights?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3a. Can we use them as a low-thrust photon engine?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n4. Lava lamps? Street lanterns?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n5. Will it crash the light-dependent mods completely?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n6. Kerbatman spotlight. For Kerbal face on the Moon.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-10-30T09:52:33Z\u0022 title=\u002210/30/2020 09:52  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 30, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by kerbiloid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}